OL,3,CFather and son lose appeals against
OL,4,Cfireworks explosion manslaughter
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FA father and son who were jailed 15
OL,8,Fyears ago following an explosion at a
OL,9,Ffireworks factory have lost challenges
OL,10,Fagainst their manslaughter convictions
OL,11,Fat the Court of Appeal.
OL,13,FMartin Winter and his son, Nathan,
OL,14,Fwere found guilty of manslaughter by
OL,15,Fgross negligence in 2009 after two
OL,16,Ffiremen died and 20 other people were
OL,17,Finjured in the blast at Marlie Farm in
OL,18,FShortgate, near Lewes, East Sussex, on
OL,19,FDecember 3 2006.
