OL,3,CFather and son lose appeals against
OL,4,Cfireworks explosion manslaughter
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FMartin Winter, who ran a fireworks
OL,8,Ffirm at the site, was handed a seven-
OL,9,Fyear jail term while his son was
OL,10,Fsentenced to five years, later reduced
OL,11,Fto four, following a five-week trial.
OL,13,FThe company was convicted of two
OL,14,Fhealth and safety breaches in
OL,15,Fconnection with the blast and was
OL,16,Ffined #30,000.
