OL,3,CFather and son lose appeals against
OL,4,Cfireworks explosion manslaughter
OL,5,Ccharges
OL,7,FAt a hearing in June, the men
OL,8,Fchallenged their convictions at the
OL,9,FCourt of Appeal in London following a
OL,10,Freferral by the Criminal Cases Review
OL,11,FCommission (CCRC), which reviews
OL,12,Fsuspected miscarriages of justice.
OL,14,FBut in a ruling on Tuesday (2 July),
OL,15,Fthree judges dismissed the appeals.
OL,17,FLord Justice William Davis, sitting
OL,18,Fwith Mrs Justice McGowan and Mrs
OL,19,FJustice Cockerill, said: "We conclude
OL,20,Fthat this appeal is misconceived and
OL,21,Fmust be dismissed."
